snippet: The attack, which targeted a compound housing people suspected of being militants, came a month after Pakistan’s new prime minister called for an end to American drone strikes.
abstract: At least 16 people are killed and five others wounded when an American drone strike hits suspected Haqqani militant compound in remote tribal region of northwestern Pakistan.

byline.original: By SALMAN MASOOD and IHSANULLAH TIPU MEHSUD

lead_paragraph: The attack, which targeted a compound housing people suspected of being militants, came a month after Pakistan’s new prime minister called for an end to American drone strikes.

headline.main: U.S. Drone Strike in Pakistan Kills at Least 16
headline.print_headline: Pakistan: Drone Strike Kills at Least 16
